e)\n| Unknown episodes\n|-\n| 2000\u201301\n| ''[[Courage the Cowardly Dog]]''\n| Spirit of the Harvest Moon <br/> The Magic Tree of Nowhere (voices)\n| 12 episodes\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[Wonder Pets!]]''\n| The Magician (voice)\n| Episode: \"The Amazing Ollie\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2010\n| ''[[Law & Order]]''\n| Judge Bertram Hill\n| Episode: \"Steel-Eyed Death\"\n|-\n| ''[[Law & Order: Special Victims Unit]]''\n| Dan Goldberg\n| Episode: \"Merchandise\"\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[Curb Your Enthusiasm]]''\n| Dr. Thurgood\n| Episode: \"Mister Softee\"\n|-\n| 2011\u201314\n| ''[[The Good Wife]]''\n| Judge Alan Karpman\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''[[30 Rock]]''\n| Jack\n| Episode: \"[[There's No I in America]]\"\n|-\n| 2013\u201314\n| ''[[The Crazy Ones]]''\n| Himself\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[Benched]]''\n| Judge Nelson\n| 5 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2015\n| ''[[Girls (TV series)|Girls]]''\n| Avi Mensusen\n| Episode: \"Tad & Loreen & Avi & Shanaz\"\n|-\n| ''[[House of Lies]]''\n| Harvey Oberholt\n| 4 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Childrens Hospital]]''\n| Leonard Hillman\n| Episode: \"With Great Power...\"\n|-\n| ''[[Married (TV series)|Married]]''\n| Professor Donald Holt\n| Episode: \"1997\"\n|-\n| 2015\u20132016\n| ''[[Blunt Talk]]''\n| Dr. Mendelson\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2015\u201318\n| ''[[Casual (TV series)|Casual]]''\n| Charles Cole\n| 8 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2016\n| ''[[New Girl (TV series)|New Girl]]''\n| J. Cronkite Valley-Forge\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[The Detour (TV series)|The Detour]]''\n| Conquistadors' Announcer (voice)\n| Episode: \"The Restaurant\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2016\u201317\n| ''[[Lady Dynamite]]''\n| Bruce Ben-Bacharach\n| 20 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Brooklyn Nine-Nine]]''\n| D.C. Parlov\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2017\n| ''[[Trial & Error (TV series)|Trial & Error]]''\n| Howard Mankiewicz\n| 2 episodes\n|-\n| ''[[Fargo (TV series)|Fargo]]''\n| Howard Zimmerman\n| Episode: \"The Law of Non-Contradiction\"\n|-\n| 2017\u20132018\n|